posting_body: ['Galtier Towers Apartments in Association with Bigos Management Presents:', 'Stop apartment searching and enjoy your summer!', 'We have a solution for you.', 'We have a 1 bedroom apartment available in the beautiful Lowertown area.', 'This apartment is the', '“Becker”', 'floorplan with', '(659)', 'Sq.', 'Ft.', 'In this apartment, you will find a great amount of counter space and a wonderful view of Downtown St. Paul.', 'Take a closer look at our apartment & community amenities!', 'Apartment Amenities:', '~Stainless Steel Appliances', '~Granite Counter Tops', '~Generous Closet Space', '~Dishwasher', '~Huge bathroom mirrors and storage items', '~Central Heat & Air', '~Updated Cabinetry', 'Community Amenities:', '~Concierge Services', '~Rooftop Pool & Hot Tub', '~Outside Movie Theater', '~Large Party Room', '~Arcade', '~Guest', 'Suites', '~And More!', 'If your curious to know more about our great apartments, contact the office and set up a tour today!', 'Ph.:', 'show contact info', '*Disclaimer: Pricing, availability and specials are determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.', '•\tdo NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers']
